entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found an Imperial Quarantine Zone. Cale has advised you to not look into it any further.
entries.journal_entry_description: Investigate a new Starport and recent building on the planet Dathomir.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to the new starport in southwest corner of Dathomir and investigate what is going on there.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find out what is going on here.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: An Imperial Quarantine Zone due to virus outbreak?  Uh, am I the only one finding a frightening correlation here? Meet me back at my home at Mos Taike.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find Cale at his place on Mos Taike, Tatooine.
